WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 20]

01:55.040 --> 01:56.050
This drought looks

01:56.920 --> 01:58.490
even worse than I expected.

01:59.200 --> 01:59.690
Right.

02:00.070 --> 02:01.130
The shops are all closed,

02:02.120 --> 02:04.420
and the townsfolk can barely get by.

02:05.120 --> 02:06.740
There's demonic energy from Han Ba everywhere.

02:08.870 --> 02:10.290
He really is clever,

02:11.430 --> 02:13.410
spreading his demonic energy all over the city.

02:14.150 --> 02:15.030
Now it's impossible to pin down

02:15.030 --> 02:16.260
his exact location.

02:18.190 --> 02:18.980
Bai Ze said

02:19.800 --> 02:21.290
that as soon as Han Ba spoke,

02:22.080 --> 02:23.850
the searing heat inside him would escape

02:24.310 --> 02:25.450
and bring drought upon the land.

02:26.750 --> 02:28.060
That's why he always kept his mouth shut

02:28.710 --> 02:29.450
and cultivated alone.

02:32.150 --> 02:33.730
Judging by the scale of this drought,

02:34.710 --> 02:35.570
Han Ba's probably

02:35.910 --> 02:37.720
turned into a chatterbox by now.

02:39.080 --> 02:39.540
By the way,

02:40.310 --> 02:41.540
did you tell You Chi

02:41.840 --> 02:43.060
about Ji Ling?

02:44.140 --> 02:44.680
Mother...

02:44.680 --> 02:45.500
Not yet.

02:45.500 --> 02:46.800
I'm hungry.

02:46.800 --> 02:47.690
I'm worried

02:47.750 --> 02:48.610
that if he finds out,

02:49.800 --> 02:51.170
every weasel in the streets

02:51.190 --> 02:52.060
will know too.

02:53.000 --> 02:54.660
That'll be no different from posting notices all over the city.

03:02.630 --> 03:02.980
See?

03:03.630 --> 03:04.540
We've only been apart for a while,

03:05.190 --> 03:06.540
and Wu Shiguang already misses me.

03:08.560 --> 03:10.400
Obviously, Wu Shiguang has ditched his friend

03:10.960 --> 03:11.950
now that he has a loved one.

03:12.790 --> 03:14.090
Why else did he dump you on me?

03:15.030 --> 03:15.970
Nonsense.

03:16.710 --> 03:18.080
I'm the unlucky one here,

03:19.240 --> 03:21.730
getting stuck with a scary brute like you

03:21.840 --> 03:22.950
to look for a place to stay.

03:25.030 --> 03:26.270
Look at this fierce face of yours.

03:27.710 --> 03:28.690
Even if we find an inn,

03:29.310 --> 03:30.540
they might not dare take us in.

03:32.590 --> 03:33.540
Have you heard of a saying?

03:33.750 --> 03:34.170
What saying?

03:36.080 --> 03:37.010
Weasel, meet your maker.

03:48.430 --> 03:49.540
There's not a soul in sight.

03:50.520 --> 03:51.990
How are we supposed to find a place to stay?

03:52.360 --> 03:53.130
Let's look around first.

03:59.590 --> 04:00.010
Here.

04:04.400 --> 04:04.850
What,

04:06.870 --> 04:07.500
you don't like it anymore?

04:10.560 --> 04:12.290
It doesn't really go with what I'm wearing today.

04:13.680 --> 04:14.780
And you think

04:15.800 --> 04:16.660
it goes well with me?

04:18.400 --> 04:19.660
Just hold it.

04:21.600 --> 04:22.290
Besides,

04:22.310 --> 04:24.020
I haven't seen Ji Ling in a very long time.

04:26.720 --> 04:28.490
Ji Ling...

04:29.190 --> 04:31.100
- All you ever talk about is Ji Ling. - Ji.

04:37.120 --> 04:38.020
Don't call me that

04:38.070 --> 04:39.050
in front of the others later.

04:39.520 --> 04:40.350
You don't like it?

04:40.870 --> 04:41.540
It's not that.

04:41.870 --> 04:43.580
It makes me sound like some half-grown kid.

04:43.680 --> 04:44.700
But it's cute.

04:48.000 --> 04:48.700
Fine.

04:49.390 --> 04:50.410
Call me whatever you like.

04:51.800 --> 04:53.410
Fair's fair.

04:53.950 --> 04:55.600
From now on, Ji, you can call me Wu too.

04:55.870 --> 04:56.590
Wu?

04:57.470 --> 04:58.530
Like the sound a fox makes?

04:59.230 --> 05:00.010
Awoo!

05:00.680 --> 05:02.580
Its name is Wu.

05:02.800 --> 05:03.250
Sorry,

05:03.560 --> 05:04.340
but the name's been taken.

05:05.510 --> 05:06.170
Master Dragon Deity,

05:06.950 --> 05:07.980
that kind of joke

05:08.070 --> 05:09.250
doesn't really suit you.

05:10.360 --> 05:11.050
Cut it out.

05:18.560 --> 05:19.660
Did Jiu Ying give you a hard time

05:20.120 --> 05:21.020
back in the Formless Moon?

05:23.720 --> 05:24.370
I'm fine.

05:25.480 --> 05:26.020
On the other hand,

05:26.820 --> 05:29.050
you used to be at each other's throats with Ji Ling,

05:29.310 --> 05:30.730
but now you two are getting along pretty well.

05:34.070 --> 05:35.170
A hundred years on the divine throne,

05:35.870 --> 05:36.810
walking on thin ice,

05:38.310 --> 05:39.580
pretending to be someone else,

05:41.000 --> 05:41.930
and living like a shadow,

05:43.240 --> 05:44.340
never able to speak the truth,

05:46.680 --> 05:47.540
he doesn't have it easy.

05:49.630 --> 05:50.730
He lived in loneliness for a century.

05:52.750 --> 05:54.280
But now that he's met Wuyi,

05:55.110 --> 05:56.690
he's got some youthful spirit back.

05:56.830 --> 05:57.880
Even the way he dresses

05:57.920 --> 05:59.170
has gotten younger.

05:59.630 --> 06:02.100
Wouldn't you call that an old tree coming back into bloom?

06:03.390 --> 06:04.580
You and Lu Wuyi

06:05.190 --> 06:06.370
are both thousand-year-old foxes.

06:07.040 --> 06:08.140
Compared to you two,

06:08.950 --> 06:09.900
Ji Ling and I

06:10.630 --> 06:11.460
are the tender shoots.

06:13.120 --> 06:15.420
You're siding with him already?

06:16.750 --> 06:19.020
People always say fox demons are heartless,

06:19.480 --> 06:22.610
but Wuyi takes love

06:23.270 --> 06:24.730
more seriously than anything.

06:25.240 --> 06:26.370
It's a blessing

06:26.510 --> 06:27.580
that he's won Wuyi's heart.

06:28.430 --> 06:30.730
Even if it comes with misfortune, he should accept it without complaint.

06:31.830 --> 06:32.540
Then what about you?

06:39.430 --> 06:40.340
You're a fox demon too.

06:44.160 --> 06:44.900
Where's your heart?

07:00.560 --> 07:01.810
Vacant rooms!

07:01.870 --> 07:03.250
Clean and comfortable rooms

07:03.270 --> 07:04.140
at fair prices!

07:04.310 --> 07:06.460
Don't miss out!

07:07.240 --> 07:08.290
A desert oasis

07:08.390 --> 07:09.540
and a spring in the wasteland,

07:09.720 --> 07:11.400
- this is the perfect haven for travelers! - With the whole city this desolate,

07:11.400 --> 07:12.930
someone's still drumming up business for an inn?

07:12.950 --> 07:13.930
It's definitely a trap.

07:28.070 --> 07:29.100
A trap?

07:30.390 --> 07:31.490
The inn is brightly lit

07:31.510 --> 07:32.370
and spotlessly clean.

07:32.480 --> 07:33.540
Don't go throwing that word around.

07:34.360 --> 07:35.580
Times are unusual right now,

07:35.600 --> 07:36.540
so we're running a special promotion.

07:36.920 --> 07:38.540
We're collecting curious stories from ordinary folk.

07:39.070 --> 07:40.410
If you two can offer us

07:40.430 --> 07:41.410
a good one,

07:42.000 --> 07:43.730
your stay is on the house.

07:44.190 --> 07:44.900
On the house?

07:47.120 --> 07:47.700
That sounds good.

07:48.310 --> 07:49.220
Where's your inn?

07:49.410 --> 07:49.850
Is it far?

07:49.850 --> 07:50.810
Not far at all.

07:51.430 --> 07:52.050
It's right here.

07:52.180 --> 07:54.420
[Chatter Inn]

07:55.070 --> 07:55.540
Wangyan!

07:55.800 --> 07:56.250
Wuyi.

07:56.560 --> 07:57.340
You're here too?

08:08.720 --> 08:09.580
What's going on?

08:11.560 --> 08:12.370
I scared him.

08:15.870 --> 08:16.980
Ji's all fair and pretty.

08:17.160 --> 08:18.220
How could he have scared anyone?

08:20.190 --> 08:21.170
Didn't we agree

08:21.190 --> 08:21.970
you wouldn't call me Ji?

08:22.000 --> 08:22.740
What's wrong,

08:22.920 --> 08:23.460
Ji?

08:24.070 --> 08:24.700
Ji?

08:27.430 --> 08:28.260
It seems

08:28.260 --> 08:29.440
the innkeeper

08:29.680 --> 08:30.540
knows Ji Ling.

08:33.190 --> 08:33.980
Of course he does.

08:34.480 --> 08:35.020
He

08:36.030 --> 08:37.250
is Han Ba.

08:41.960 --> 08:42.580
Is that so?

08:42.960 --> 08:43.420
Ji...

08:50.510 --> 08:51.220
I'm exhausted.

08:52.720 --> 08:53.420
I can't do this anymore.

08:54.480 --> 08:55.010
I can't.

08:55.910 --> 08:56.820
My legs are about to give out.

08:57.910 --> 08:59.010
You go find an inn.

08:59.960 --> 09:01.380
I'll just curl up in some hole by the road.

09:01.720 --> 09:02.180
No way.

09:03.360 --> 09:04.100
Then carry me.

09:11.720 --> 09:12.250
Listen.

09:13.120 --> 09:13.650
Walk on your own.

09:13.910 --> 09:14.490
I'm not carrying you.

09:14.750 --> 09:15.370
What?

09:16.030 --> 09:17.250
Listen. Don't turn around.

09:18.240 --> 09:19.060
There's a girl

09:19.480 --> 09:20.370
following me

09:20.840 --> 09:21.490
and sneaking looks at me.

09:23.970 --> 09:24.580
Hey!

09:24.960 --> 09:26.130
Get back here. What are you doing?

09:27.550 --> 09:28.530
She's following me.

09:29.510 --> 09:30.420
What nonsense.

09:30.670 --> 09:31.300
She's not blind.

09:32.120 --> 09:33.490
It's obvious which of us

09:34.030 --> 09:35.060
is more handsome.

09:37.480 --> 09:39.340
Miss, I'm You...

09:39.550 --> 09:41.220
Are you the one

09:41.240 --> 09:42.890
who used to be by Master Chi Wen's side?

09:45.720 --> 09:46.340
I'm Li Jie.

09:47.860 --> 09:49.730
Do... do you still remember me?

09:55.910 --> 09:57.250
Master Chi Wen,

09:57.910 --> 10:01.010
please... please watch over my great-grandmother.

10:01.510 --> 10:04.890
Please let her get better soon.

10:20.030 --> 10:21.820
Please... please let her

10:22.150 --> 10:24.370
recover quickly.

10:26.480 --> 10:27.420
Please.

10:32.270 --> 10:34.100
Master Chi Wen sent me to pass a message on to you.

10:35.510 --> 10:37.010
Your long vigil and prayers here

10:37.480 --> 10:39.130
show a devotion heaven and earth can witness.

10:39.630 --> 10:40.770
But birth, aging, sickness, and death

10:41.390 --> 10:42.820
are the ways of the world.

10:43.510 --> 10:44.700
Every mortal life

10:44.750 --> 10:45.850
has its end.

10:47.390 --> 10:48.420
The Dragon Deity's Power

10:49.240 --> 10:51.180
cannot be used to reverse the laws of nature.

10:54.240 --> 10:55.650
Instead of wasting your time

10:56.600 --> 10:57.730
kneeling here in prayer,

10:58.910 --> 11:00.250
you should spend more time with your family

11:01.120 --> 11:02.100
and cherish the days you have.

11:03.670 --> 11:05.370
Does the Master Dragon Deity know

11:06.440 --> 11:08.060
about all the suffering in this world?

11:11.910 --> 11:12.460
He does.

11:14.550 --> 11:15.940
Then does he just ignore it all?

11:18.910 --> 11:20.180
Master Dragon Deity said

11:22.440 --> 11:24.060
what carries us through suffering

11:24.720 --> 11:25.890
and helps us overcome evil

11:27.390 --> 11:28.700
is not the protection of the gods,

11:29.730 --> 11:30.880
but the hope and courage

11:31.840 --> 11:33.300
that never fade

11:34.550 --> 11:35.490
from our hearts.

11:42.530 --> 11:43.700
He asked me

11:43.840 --> 11:44.820
to return this to you.

11:53.320 --> 11:54.980
Do you remember this?

11:58.150 --> 11:58.610
I do.

12:02.360 --> 12:03.130
Master Dragon Deity,

12:04.000 --> 12:05.770
have you come to take back the Dragon Deity's Power?

12:08.030 --> 12:09.220
And you're telling me

12:09.910 --> 12:10.890
this man is a dragon,

12:13.000 --> 12:15.940
and these two are foxes over 1,000 years old?

12:16.960 --> 12:19.010
This is too much for me.

12:19.600 --> 12:20.650
I only wanted to run

12:20.670 --> 12:21.650
a small business

12:21.670 --> 12:22.500
and keep an inn.

12:22.750 --> 12:24.520
Why send

12:24.520 --> 12:25.940
such a force

12:26.080 --> 12:27.420
to come after me?

12:28.120 --> 12:29.220
Luo'an is parched with drought.

12:29.220 --> 12:30.010
Why do you think?

12:30.380 --> 12:31.610
Why did you run into the inn and hide?

12:32.870 --> 12:33.700
Did you think that door

12:33.720 --> 12:34.700
would keep me out?

12:35.380 --> 12:36.790
Why's the inn door busted?

12:37.030 --> 12:37.770
Did some bandit barge in

12:37.790 --> 12:39.460
and start looting and killing?

12:39.840 --> 12:40.270
Don't be scared.

12:40.480 --> 12:41.490
I'll take care of them!

12:45.150 --> 12:45.890
You're all here?

12:47.440 --> 12:48.650
You beat us again.

12:58.360 --> 12:59.220
My eyes

12:59.510 --> 13:00.340
are quite alluring.

13:09.200 --> 13:09.890
What are you all doing?

13:10.270 --> 13:11.220
Why is the mood so tense?

13:12.120 --> 13:12.650
Forcing...

13:16.360 --> 13:18.060
asking someone to hand over the Dragon Deity's Power.

13:20.600 --> 13:21.700
Are you afraid

13:21.910 --> 13:23.370
that once you hand it over,

13:23.750 --> 13:24.370
you'll die?

13:29.870 --> 13:31.060
These extra years I've lived,

13:31.080 --> 13:32.010
propped up by the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:32.440 --> 13:34.370
were stolen to begin with.

13:35.790 --> 13:36.580
I'm not afraid of dying.

13:38.550 --> 13:39.610
What I'm afraid of

13:42.080 --> 13:43.890
is that once I hand over the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:44.600 --> 13:45.890
the searing heat inside me

13:46.120 --> 13:47.300
will spiral out of control,

13:48.440 --> 13:49.460
and drought will break out

13:52.240 --> 13:53.250
across the whole world.

13:55.030 --> 13:56.490
Once we gather all of the Dragon Deity's Power,

13:58.390 --> 13:59.610
he can become a true dragon,

14:00.120 --> 14:00.850
summon wind and rain,

14:01.720 --> 14:02.580
and end the drought.

14:04.510 --> 14:05.300
Helping him become a dragon

14:06.080 --> 14:07.420
was also Master Chi Wen's wish.

14:08.510 --> 14:09.460
Master Chi Wen?

14:09.840 --> 14:10.730
Is everyone

14:10.750 --> 14:12.530
talking about themselves in the third person now?

14:14.630 --> 14:15.820
So you're the Tenth Dragon Son

14:15.820 --> 14:17.130
we've all been waiting for?

14:18.270 --> 14:18.820
That's right.

14:21.870 --> 14:22.250
What is it?

14:23.270 --> 14:23.850
Don't I look the part?

14:23.880 --> 14:24.750
I wouldn't dare say that.

14:26.010 --> 14:27.180
I just didn't expect

14:27.440 --> 14:29.520
the Tenth Dragon Son to look so utterly ordinary.

14:29.750 --> 14:30.770
You've hidden it well.

14:32.790 --> 14:33.180
See?

14:33.440 --> 14:34.370
I told you.

14:35.200 --> 14:36.530
You should've bought some nicer outfits.

14:37.390 --> 14:38.340
Look at Ji Ling.

14:38.610 --> 14:39.820
He dresses so flamboyantly every day.

14:40.600 --> 14:41.420
I heard that.

14:42.080 --> 14:43.700
Both of my ears heard every word.

14:47.870 --> 14:48.530
These past years,

14:50.080 --> 14:51.580
my injuries have only worsened.

14:52.910 --> 14:54.340
The only thing that can suppress

14:55.030 --> 14:56.490
the searing heat inside me is the Dragon Deity's Power.

14:57.670 --> 14:58.580
I didn't take back my power

14:59.120 --> 15:00.010
to break the oath,

15:00.870 --> 15:02.100
but to suppress the searing heat.

15:04.960 --> 15:05.980
Are your injuries

15:07.390 --> 15:08.610
really incurable?

15:13.840 --> 15:14.370
That's why

15:15.910 --> 15:16.940
this drought befell Luo'an.

15:18.520 --> 15:19.730
I see.

15:20.390 --> 15:21.730
But Luo'an was doomed to drought.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.950
Even if you had kept your mouth shut,

15:24.150 --> 15:25.760
it wouldn't have changed anything.

15:27.630 --> 15:28.820
I only started talking

15:30.360 --> 15:32.340
to fulfill a young girl's wish.

15:38.260 --> 15:43.380
♪The wind blows by, and memories sway with dreams♪

15:44.300 --> 15:49.300
♪I stay silent, afraid the fire in my heart will rise♪

15:50.860 --> 15:54.060
♪Reed flowers sway with burning heat♪

15:54.300 --> 15:57.500
♪Shaking the story into something blurred and worn♪

15:57.740 --> 15:59.740
♪I am only♪

15:59.860 --> 16:02.900
♪A murmuring traveler through wind and snow♪

16:05.100 --> 16:10.380
♪Watching the evening glow turn cold and fade into night♪

16:11.740 --> 16:16.780
♪Watching every stroke and mark spell out reluctance♪

16:18.340 --> 16:21.500
♪Watching spider lilies bloom across the hills♪

16:21.660 --> 16:24.980
♪Watching the one in my dreams send back bitterness...♪

16:25.720 --> 16:26.890
She's the girl I was talking about.

16:28.320 --> 16:29.130
Her name is Mu Long.

16:31.390 --> 16:32.330
These are all stories

16:32.330 --> 16:34.300
she and I collected by waiving lodging fees.

16:35.440 --> 16:37.620
I want to help Mu Long finish her story collection.

16:38.120 --> 16:40.010
All that's missing now is an ending.

16:42.320 --> 16:43.340
I've watched

16:43.390 --> 16:44.580
Mu Long grow up.

16:45.200 --> 16:46.250
Since childhood, she's had a stutter,

16:46.750 --> 16:47.370
kept to herself,

16:47.600 --> 16:48.770
and struggled to get along with people.

16:49.600 --> 16:51.220
The only thing that can make her speak

16:51.720 --> 16:53.300
is when it concerns this collection of stories.

16:55.150 --> 16:56.610
I have to help her finish it.

16:59.960 --> 17:00.820
Masters and madams,

17:01.240 --> 17:02.100
please give me one more day.

17:02.720 --> 17:03.580
Just one more day.

17:04.750 --> 17:05.220
Tomorrow,

17:06.320 --> 17:07.980
I will return the Dragon Deity's Power.

17:18.400 --> 17:18.900
Do you...

17:19.440 --> 17:21.420
do you really have good stories?

17:29.880 --> 17:30.290
All right!

17:31.160 --> 17:32.290
Based on how good

17:32.310 --> 17:33.810
your stories were,

17:34.070 --> 17:35.420
I've assigned your rooms.

17:36.070 --> 17:37.810
From the most luxurious to the most modest,

17:37.960 --> 17:40.420
they're divided into Heaven, Earth,

17:40.680 --> 17:41.290
and Human tiers.

17:41.990 --> 17:42.680
Sleep well,

17:43.450 --> 17:44.010
everyone.

17:58.400 --> 17:58.940
Han Ba,

17:59.550 --> 18:01.420
how dare you put Master Dragon Deity in a Human-tier room?

18:15.160 --> 18:15.770
An Earth-tier room?

18:16.550 --> 18:17.010
Got a problem?

18:24.400 --> 18:25.140
We need two rooms.

18:49.310 --> 18:50.570
As I recall,

18:51.200 --> 18:53.140
this lady didn't tell a story just now.

18:53.720 --> 18:55.180
Are you planning to sleep on the street tonight?

18:56.960 --> 18:58.140
I only tell my stories

18:58.270 --> 18:59.530
to the one I love.

19:01.640 --> 19:02.050
Go on.

19:02.750 --> 19:04.250
I don't mind being the one you love.

19:06.240 --> 19:07.310
But I do.

19:08.050 --> 19:09.460
I already have someone I love.

19:10.270 --> 19:11.460
He is the one I love,

19:12.550 --> 19:13.570
and that's settled for life.

19:15.310 --> 19:16.770
I already have someone I love.

19:17.240 --> 19:19.140
He is the one I love,

19:19.550 --> 19:20.670
and that's settled for life.

19:25.960 --> 19:27.250
Then the most comfortable Heaven-tier suite

19:28.160 --> 19:28.700
belongs to you.

19:32.310 --> 19:32.980
Thank you, sir.

19:42.750 --> 19:43.250
Here.

19:45.070 --> 19:46.620
I don't accept charity.

19:49.070 --> 19:49.980
Drop the act.

19:51.110 --> 19:52.460
Could you save a little face for me?

20:20.820 --> 20:21.530
What are you doing?

20:22.960 --> 20:24.380
Someone's unhappy.

20:24.380 --> 20:25.700
I need to cheer him up.

20:27.830 --> 20:28.180
I'm good.

20:32.240 --> 20:33.600
Why are you being petty?

20:34.080 --> 20:35.620
I am broad-minded.

20:36.590 --> 20:38.330
I just think this wine tastes

20:40.920 --> 20:41.460
very sour.

20:43.920 --> 20:44.490
Sour?

20:48.400 --> 20:49.460
How is it sour?

20:49.640 --> 20:50.330
You're way sourer.

20:52.310 --> 20:52.770
Well?

20:53.550 --> 20:54.010
Is it sweet?

20:55.720 --> 20:56.250
It is.

20:59.550 --> 21:00.420
I think it's sweet too.

21:03.880 --> 21:04.810
A Heaven-tier room.

21:09.240 --> 21:12.220
Yunjin brocade, silk bedding, and incense.

21:13.840 --> 21:14.870
Who would've thought

21:15.830 --> 21:17.620
that gaudy, flashy stuff like this

21:18.550 --> 21:20.090
would be enough to make you so happy?

21:23.920 --> 21:25.860
Back at the Shilin Sect,

21:26.240 --> 21:26.980
someone prepared

21:27.000 --> 21:28.490
all this for me too.

21:28.610 --> 21:29.520
Who was it?

21:34.350 --> 21:36.410
And I remember someone saying...

21:36.710 --> 21:38.330
I don't accept charity.

21:38.920 --> 21:41.180
Don't think you can wear down my resolve

21:42.400 --> 21:44.220
with fine clothes and good food.

21:45.750 --> 21:46.380
Who was that?

21:48.270 --> 21:49.290
Why do you know everything?

21:50.880 --> 21:52.010
Does everyone in the Shilin Sect

21:52.070 --> 21:53.640
have special sight and hearing?

21:54.790 --> 21:55.590
Take a guess.

21:57.680 --> 21:58.250
Take a guess?

22:02.030 --> 22:02.460
You tell me.

22:04.350 --> 22:05.390
Are you going to tell me or not?

22:07.170 --> 22:08.150
It won't tell me.

22:09.640 --> 22:10.810
Then don't force it.

22:11.650 --> 22:12.420
Then you tell me.

22:13.030 --> 22:13.900
Then go on and ask it.

22:13.960 --> 22:14.700
I don't remember either.

22:16.460 --> 22:17.130
Tell me!

22:18.120 --> 22:19.170
Yes, you.

22:19.250 --> 22:19.910
Say it!

22:39.220 --> 22:44.060
♪A silent parting spreads like a sea of fog♪

22:45.260 --> 22:49.100
♪How do you say goodbye without regret?♪

22:51.060 --> 22:56.460
♪If even longing for an ordinary life is folly♪

22:57.060 --> 23:01.260
♪Who is still whispering, stranded in the river of time?♪

23:02.380 --> 23:08.500
♪Watch the spring breeze stir the warm sun, flowers across the hills♪

23:08.860 --> 23:14.660
♪Summer days run long, and flowing rain carries me afar♪

23:15.300 --> 23:20.820
♪Autumn turns cool, and fallen leaves become the clothes of dreams♪

23:21.260 --> 23:27.300
♪A face worn old by wind, snow, and frost♪

23:28.340 --> 23:33.100
♪The opening of the story is but a blank line♪

23:34.540 --> 23:38.660
♪The ending in disarray, like youth drawing to a close♪

23:43.340 --> 23:45.380
♪Eyes brim with tears♪

23:49.260 --> 23:50.580
♪Don't forget♪

24:00.750 --> 24:02.120
May I have a look?

24:03.200 --> 24:03.860
No.

24:03.860 --> 24:06.260
Not even Mr. Yan has read any of these.

24:06.830 --> 24:08.860
No one gets to read my stories

24:08.920 --> 24:09.980
until I've finished all of them.

24:13.500 --> 24:15.490
Why do you like writing stories?

24:16.650 --> 24:18.100
My great-grandmother

24:18.100 --> 24:20.310
used to tell me stories all the time.

24:21.640 --> 24:21.980
She...

24:22.240 --> 24:23.090
she always said

24:23.270 --> 24:24.220
that since I stuttered,

24:24.510 --> 24:27.660
writing stories suited me better.

24:29.480 --> 24:30.700
Too bad

24:31.440 --> 24:31.860
she...

24:32.270 --> 24:33.530
she'll never get to read them.

24:37.400 --> 24:38.490
Everything in this world

24:38.880 --> 24:39.810
fades away eventually.

24:40.510 --> 24:41.620
But there's a saying:

24:42.790 --> 24:45.220
"Writers never truly die."

24:46.270 --> 24:47.530
As long as their stories are read,

24:48.030 --> 24:49.100
the days

24:49.110 --> 24:51.090
they wrote down can be relived again.

24:52.640 --> 24:54.380
Your great-grandmother must be in your stories, right?

24:55.440 --> 24:56.460
Then she will always

24:56.480 --> 24:57.860
exist in this world.

24:59.880 --> 25:01.810
She said that too.

25:02.480 --> 25:03.490
Stories

25:04.240 --> 25:05.980
can weave the wishes

25:06.480 --> 25:08.770
people dare not speak of

25:09.510 --> 25:11.700
and their regrets

25:12.750 --> 25:15.380
into dreams of fiction.

25:15.880 --> 25:16.940
The people in stories

25:17.920 --> 25:19.330
never die.

25:20.110 --> 25:21.420
I wonder whether my regret

25:23.240 --> 25:24.770
will ever have a happy ending.

25:28.920 --> 25:29.290
Here, Miss Mu.

25:30.550 --> 25:31.700
Th... thank you.

25:35.680 --> 25:37.330
Your regret?

25:38.200 --> 25:39.490
Do... do you mean

25:40.070 --> 25:41.620
the girl in your story today,

25:42.640 --> 25:44.710
the one who made you a bracelet?

25:50.790 --> 25:51.450
Yes.

25:52.440 --> 25:53.290
It's a pity.

25:54.750 --> 25:55.700
My bracelet broke.

25:57.400 --> 25:58.050
I'm waiting for her.

25:59.240 --> 26:00.290
And I hope that one day,

26:01.110 --> 26:02.180
she'll be willing

26:02.510 --> 26:03.490
to make me another bracelet.

26:06.000 --> 26:06.900
No... no,

26:07.480 --> 26:08.420
that's not right.

26:09.590 --> 26:10.050
Why not?

26:13.070 --> 26:14.500
Because this is

26:14.520 --> 26:15.970
your story.

26:16.320 --> 26:17.500
You... you can't just wait.

26:17.680 --> 26:19.130
You need to write it yourself

26:19.910 --> 26:21.570
to get the ending you want.

26:22.510 --> 26:22.970
You...

26:23.400 --> 26:25.970
you can make a bracelet yourself.

27:28.350 --> 27:29.250
Ji Ling, you've really

27:30.270 --> 27:31.290
got a petty streak.

27:32.270 --> 27:33.420
I shared good food and wine with you,

27:34.030 --> 27:34.980
and you're still ignoring me.

28:24.920 --> 28:25.770
Big drumstick.

28:25.880 --> 28:26.700
Big drumstick.

28:26.920 --> 28:27.940
Big drumstick.

28:29.960 --> 28:30.620
Miss Mu?

28:32.880 --> 28:33.740
She's asleep.

28:39.510 --> 28:40.180
Let me take a look.

28:46.960 --> 28:49.490
"The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate."

28:49.510 --> 28:50.220
What kind of writing is this?

28:50.220 --> 28:51.160
[The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate]

28:51.160 --> 28:51.860
It's so ugly.

28:56.240 --> 28:56.900
Miss Mu Long...

28:57.030 --> 28:58.150
What are you doing?

28:58.680 --> 28:59.160
You...

28:59.200 --> 29:01.620
- you've stained my manuscript! - I'm sorry.

29:01.960 --> 29:03.140
I forgot my hands were covered in grease.

29:03.480 --> 29:04.250
Don't worry...

29:05.420 --> 29:06.990
Hey, don't cry.

29:07.510 --> 29:08.090
I know.

29:08.110 --> 29:08.860
I'll go find Wangyan.

29:09.160 --> 29:10.010
She knows magic.

29:10.480 --> 29:11.380
I'll go get her right now.

29:11.960 --> 29:12.570
Wangyan!

29:13.160 --> 29:14.140
Help, Wangyan!

29:14.440 --> 29:15.940
Wangyan, where are you?

29:16.790 --> 29:18.420
Wangyan, help!

29:18.420 --> 29:19.250
Wangyan!

29:19.660 --> 29:20.620
Wangyan!

29:22.420 --> 29:23.250
Wangyan!

29:27.030 --> 29:27.940
Wangyan!

29:43.000 --> 29:43.490
Wangyan...

30:04.960 --> 30:05.570
Ji Ling,

30:06.480 --> 30:07.860
why did you do this?

30:13.400 --> 30:14.770
You can go kill Chi Wen now.

30:38.680 --> 30:40.010
Wu Shiguang is under Jiu Ying's control.

30:42.170 --> 30:44.130
You really did keep your promise.

30:45.240 --> 30:46.520
Now you can sit

30:48.030 --> 30:50.000
on the Dragon Deity's throne

30:50.960 --> 30:51.940
forever.

30:57.830 --> 30:59.460
You killed my sister.

31:01.510 --> 31:03.090
I'll never forgive you.

31:20.240 --> 31:20.900
It was a dream.

31:32.030 --> 31:32.570
Mu Long.

31:43.960 --> 31:44.420
How?

31:57.750 --> 31:59.090
Not even the Dragon Deity's Power could...

31:59.510 --> 32:00.940
This person doesn't seem to fear magic.

32:13.640 --> 32:14.380
Who was that?

32:14.880 --> 32:15.700
Why did they know

32:15.720 --> 32:16.490
my bladework so well?

32:16.680 --> 32:17.490
They didn't know it,

32:18.270 --> 32:18.980
but they could predict

32:19.000 --> 32:19.900
every strike you made.

32:20.510 --> 32:21.620
What in the world is going on?

32:23.480 --> 32:24.290
There's only

32:25.750 --> 32:26.420
one person I know

32:28.510 --> 32:29.420
who's capable of that.

32:33.880 --> 32:34.860
Where are Ji Ling and Lu Wuyi?

32:38.400 --> 32:39.010
Master Dragon Deity.

32:40.750 --> 32:41.380
Master Dragon Deity?

32:57.070 --> 32:57.660
Wuyi.

32:58.680 --> 32:59.330
Wuyi?

33:04.350 --> 33:05.490
Master Dragon Deity isn't in his room.

33:07.590 --> 33:08.660
Is Lu Wuyi gone too?

33:17.590 --> 33:18.010
Li Jie,

33:18.960 --> 33:19.810
what are you doing?

33:31.600 --> 33:32.930
Were you two

33:33.590 --> 33:35.030
in the room the whole time?

33:35.830 --> 33:36.570
Wangyan...

34:05.790 --> 34:06.330
Wu,

34:08.000 --> 34:09.380
what in the world is going on?

34:12.190 --> 34:13.130
What are you trying to do?

34:23.590 --> 34:24.050
Mu Long?

34:26.230 --> 34:26.690
Mu Long?

34:34.880 --> 34:36.690
If Mu Long can't go back to normal,

34:38.920 --> 34:39.820
none of you are getting

34:39.840 --> 34:41.090
the Dragon Deity's Power.

34:41.760 --> 34:42.820
Are you threatening us?

34:44.030 --> 34:44.740
I know.

34:45.760 --> 34:46.690
There's no way I can beat

34:47.440 --> 34:48.860
two foxes from the Formless Moon

34:48.920 --> 34:49.740
and two dragons.

34:50.760 --> 34:51.820
But I've already

34:52.150 --> 34:53.420
hidden away the Dragon Deity's Power.

34:54.360 --> 34:55.740
If you don't save Mu Long...

34:56.280 --> 34:56.860
We will.

35:00.920 --> 35:01.820
I can try.

35:03.320 --> 35:04.860
She's under Word Magic.

35:15.920 --> 35:16.530
Master Dragon Deity,

35:17.190 --> 35:18.610
a person in black attacked Mu Long just now.

35:24.150 --> 35:25.490
Go investigate with Wu Shiguang

35:26.150 --> 35:26.820
and the others.

35:28.360 --> 35:28.900
What about you?

35:29.960 --> 35:30.940
Don't you need me with you?

35:32.530 --> 35:34.380
I have something more important to do.

35:37.800 --> 35:38.340
Understood.

36:00.110 --> 36:02.170
I can't wake her.

36:05.510 --> 36:06.440
Whoever cast the spell

36:06.710 --> 36:08.060
is stronger than I am.

36:08.590 --> 36:10.410
But Word Magic is the Formless Moon's specialty.

36:10.670 --> 36:11.610
Besides someone from the Formless Moon,

36:11.960 --> 36:13.010
who would know this spell?

36:15.960 --> 36:16.490
Xiaowei.

36:17.440 --> 36:18.210
Xiaowei?

36:20.030 --> 36:20.980
You mean Ji Ling?

36:21.840 --> 36:23.210
How dare you suspect Master Dragon Deity?

36:26.960 --> 36:27.650
He can use

36:27.670 --> 36:29.130
Xiaowei's spells through his Spirit-Binding Ring.

36:29.480 --> 36:30.530
Of course I suspect him.

36:31.230 --> 36:32.420
But didn't you just say

36:33.670 --> 36:35.130
Ji Ling was with your sister?

36:36.550 --> 36:37.570
Maybe Wuyi

36:37.920 --> 36:39.130
was helping Ji Ling cover it up.

36:40.280 --> 36:41.860
With all that fighting in the front courtyard,

36:42.550 --> 36:43.650
how could the Dragon Deity

36:44.000 --> 36:45.260
not have heard anything?

36:47.400 --> 36:47.860
Wangyan,

36:48.550 --> 36:50.210
why do you suspect Ji Ling so much?

36:51.400 --> 36:52.420
Do you know something?

36:59.830 --> 37:00.560
No.

37:01.960 --> 37:02.680
I just think

37:02.680 --> 37:04.450
the person in black was too strong.

37:04.670 --> 37:06.090
Even together, we couldn't beat them.

37:07.360 --> 37:07.900
Commander Li,

37:08.550 --> 37:09.490
aside from Ji Ling,

37:09.880 --> 37:11.820
who else knows your bladework that well?

37:22.800 --> 37:24.420
Why don't you suspect Lu Wuyi?

37:28.190 --> 37:28.690
You said

37:29.280 --> 37:30.420
she was covering up for Ji Ling.

37:31.230 --> 37:32.900
Why couldn't it be Ji Ling covering for her instead?

37:36.230 --> 37:37.010
You also said to me...

37:37.360 --> 37:38.170
There's only

37:38.840 --> 37:39.690
one person I know

37:41.590 --> 37:42.780
who's capable of that.

37:44.030 --> 37:45.210
Were you referring

37:46.880 --> 37:48.090
to Lu Wuyi?

37:50.960 --> 37:51.460
Listen.

37:52.320 --> 37:53.530
Is it possible

37:54.670 --> 37:56.610
that both of you are wrong?

37:57.550 --> 37:58.780
What if the two of them were working together

37:59.880 --> 38:01.300
and covering for each other?

38:04.800 --> 38:05.770
What secret is hidden

38:05.770 --> 38:06.720
in the first chapter of this manuscript?

38:07.840 --> 38:09.650
Why would the person in black go to such lengths over it?

38:13.190 --> 38:14.090
I haven't read it either.

38:15.320 --> 38:16.650
Mu Long said no one was allowed to read it

38:17.030 --> 38:17.980
until it was finished.

38:20.590 --> 38:22.340
Maybe it has something to do with my memories.

38:25.920 --> 38:27.090
Do you know me?

38:34.360 --> 38:35.860
So you're finally willing to talk about this.

38:37.070 --> 38:38.650
I thought you were pretending not to know me

38:39.670 --> 38:41.010
because there was something you couldn't say.

38:42.070 --> 38:43.460
I even played along with you.

38:47.630 --> 38:48.690
You really don't remember?

38:51.030 --> 38:52.050
Jiu Ying tampered

38:52.070 --> 38:52.820
with my memories.

38:53.480 --> 38:54.420
Any memories I had of you

38:55.280 --> 38:56.090
are gone.

38:58.400 --> 38:59.820
Little Pomegranate...

39:01.360 --> 39:02.300
Little Pomegranate...

39:03.480 --> 39:04.610
Little Pomegranate?

39:05.030 --> 39:05.940
What did Miss Mu say?

39:08.230 --> 39:09.300
Little Pomegranate?

39:11.760 --> 39:12.780
- What was it again? - What,

39:13.710 --> 39:14.420
itching for a beating again?

39:15.550 --> 39:16.650
Want me to scratch you with my blade?

39:16.760 --> 39:17.530
Be quiet.

39:18.400 --> 39:19.380
I'm almost remembering it.

39:21.920 --> 39:23.130
Let me show you a place.

39:24.000 --> 39:24.690
Maybe

39:25.360 --> 39:26.300
it will clear things up.

39:28.400 --> 39:29.090
And maybe

39:30.320 --> 39:31.570
it'll help you remember something too.

39:55.150 --> 39:56.280
Thank you.

40:02.630 --> 40:04.090
Sister, higher.

40:04.960 --> 40:06.570
Sister, higher!

40:14.440 --> 40:14.860
What is it?

40:17.920 --> 40:18.490
Nothing.

40:39.630 --> 40:41.380
This used to be Mu Long's great-grandmother's home,

40:42.400 --> 40:43.940
where she lived as a child.

40:46.960 --> 40:47.690
Where she lived?

40:52.630 --> 40:53.380
I remember now!

40:53.480 --> 40:54.260
You scared me.

40:54.480 --> 40:55.020
The manuscript!

40:55.230 --> 40:56.420
The first chapter of that manuscript

40:56.960 --> 40:58.210
was Little Pomegranate's story.

40:59.030 --> 40:59.860
The moment I heard

40:59.880 --> 41:00.900
the words "Little Pomegranate,"

41:01.590 --> 41:02.130
I felt like I'd

41:03.230 --> 41:04.010
seen them somewhere before.

41:05.110 --> 41:07.570
"The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate."

41:07.690 --> 41:08.770
[The Great Demon and Little Pomegranate]
What kind of writing is this?

41:09.110 --> 41:09.740
It's so ugly.

41:10.510 --> 41:11.260
The handwriting

41:11.630 --> 41:13.010
was all crooked.

41:13.190 --> 41:13.690
It was ugly.

41:15.400 --> 41:15.940
Really ugly.

41:17.590 --> 41:18.260
But still, I recognized

41:18.280 --> 41:19.480
the words "Little" and "Pomegranate."

41:20.030 --> 41:20.690
But

41:21.710 --> 41:22.900
Mu Long's handwriting is very neat.

41:23.440 --> 41:24.490
How could it be crooked?

41:25.480 --> 41:26.380
She had too much to drink.

41:27.110 --> 41:27.820
Shut it.

41:52.030 --> 41:53.650
Little Pomegranate.

42:00.630 --> 42:01.610
Little Pomegranate?

42:02.000 --> 42:02.760
Why does Little Pomegranate

42:02.760 --> 42:04.070
look like she's crying?

42:08.360 --> 42:09.490
Isn't that Wangyan?

42:19.630 --> 42:20.190
This...

42:21.320 --> 42:22.220
this really is me.

42:24.400 --> 42:26.140
But why would I be in this painting?

42:27.590 --> 42:29.340
And that tall, handsome fellow in the back

42:30.630 --> 42:31.380
is Mr. Yan.

42:32.630 --> 42:33.210
The painter is

42:33.670 --> 42:34.300
Cui Jun.

42:36.670 --> 42:37.570
Who's Cui Jun?

42:39.510 --> 42:40.210
Maybe

42:41.710 --> 42:42.570
I can try something.

43:07.320 --> 43:08.370
Where did Wu Shiguang and Wangyan go?

43:08.630 --> 43:09.900
How did they disappear in the blink of an eye?

43:11.400 --> 43:12.610
They've gone into the painting.

43:13.320 --> 43:14.420
Why did they leave me behind?

43:15.400 --> 43:16.260
What good would you do?

43:16.590 --> 43:17.300
What good would I do?

43:18.030 --> 43:18.900
I figured it out already.

43:20.150 --> 43:21.140
The girl in the painting

43:21.230 --> 43:21.980
is Little Pomegranate.

43:22.440 --> 43:23.360
And this story

43:23.440 --> 43:24.810
must have something to do with Mr. Yan.

43:25.280 --> 43:26.260
As for the great demon,

43:27.070 --> 43:27.610
that's you,

43:28.510 --> 43:29.130
Han Ba!

43:30.280 --> 43:30.650
Am I right?

43:32.840 --> 43:33.460
Pretty sharp, aren't I?

43:35.670 --> 43:36.460
Good for you.

43:37.590 --> 43:39.050
You've figured out what everyone already knows.

43:42.880 --> 43:44.210
Your story with Little Pomegranate

43:44.400 --> 43:45.300
must've been full of longing

43:45.320 --> 43:45.940
and heartbreak.

43:46.550 --> 43:47.420
Come on, tell us already.

43:53.840 --> 43:54.490
My name is Su Jian.

43:54.840 --> 43:56.090
What's your name?

43:58.000 --> 43:59.210
Why won't you say anything?

43:59.280 --> 44:01.380
You won't even tell me your name?

44:16.780 --> 44:17.940
♪It's your light♪

44:18.140 --> 44:20.020
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:20.180 --> 44:23.300
♪That set the night alight♪

44:23.660 --> 44:30.180
♪And lead me through the fight♪

44:31.940 --> 44:33.820
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

44:34.260 --> 44:38.700
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

44:39.500 --> 44:41.180
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

44:41.340 --> 44:46.740
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

44:47.500 --> 44:52.900
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

44:55.220 --> 45:01.260
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

45:02.220 --> 45:04.380
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:04.660 --> 45:09.500
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:09.860 --> 45:12.180
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:12.380 --> 45:17.460
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

45:17.700 --> 45:19.700
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

45:19.980 --> 45:24.340
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

45:25.340 --> 45:32.300
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

45:48.860 --> 45:51.820
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

45:52.900 --> 45:56.300
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

45:57.100 --> 45:59.620
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

45:59.860 --> 46:02.940
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

46:03.340 --> 46:05.660
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:06.180 --> 46:10.580
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:10.820 --> 46:12.980
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

46:13.380 --> 46:18.340
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

46:18.580 --> 46:19.740
♪It's your light♪

46:19.940 --> 46:21.780
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

46:21.980 --> 46:25.100
♪That set the night alight♪

46:25.860 --> 46:35.300
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
